reviewText: very good anime. not for everyone. can be intense depending on the situation.
It came really quickly and between two cardboard cutouts to not damage the case. It came with the 2 art cards inside. No scratches on the dvd and it plays.
bought this for my daughter who is obsessed with this series. the price was amazing and was brand new as indicated. also was ship and received fast

Hell Girl has done a remarkable job thus far. Besides a short stumble with the introduction of the character Gilles, this series has continued to tell an incredibly complex and compelling story. Pushed forward by a cast of believable characters and leaving the audience asking questions, the ending of this series is easily one of my most anticipated. Very highly recommended.
